strings: <voice_0x010009C4><se_low>*: When I went, there were hardly any tourists!
<voice_0x010009C5><se_low>*: Yes, may I ask you a question?
<voice_0x010009CC><se_low>*: I also think so. In other words, you have to have enough time to achieve it.
<voice_0x010009CD><se_low>*: But I don't want to convince you.
<voice_0x010009CE><se_low>*: which one? Have you changed your mind about not helping me?
<voice_0x010009C6><se_low>*: I'm only going to say this one time, so listen up.
<voice_0x010009C7><se_low>*: At the top of the hill you can see a tree with red leaves.
<voice_0x010009C8><se_low>*: The last time I walked, I moved a little. However, it seems he forgot to bring his tool bag.
<voice_0x010009C9><se_low>*: I don't expect you to do this for free. We give you a gift.
<voice_0x010009CA><se_low>*: I'll be waiting for you in the cabin to welcome them. try not to exaggerate
<voice_0x010009CF><se_low>*: so you don't get my point? I told it once and I explained it!
<voice_0x010009D2><se_low>*: You can't throw the dupatta like that. sorry if you can help me
<voice_0x010009D3><se_low>*: But what you left under the red tree, I want to get back. You can see it with your own eyes from the top of the mountain.
<voice_0x010009D4><se_low>*: I'll give you a small reward if you help me get here.
